## What Results Can I Expect from Local SEO?

Local SEO results typically appear within 2-4 months for competitive terms. Initial improvements come from Google Business Profile optimisation and citation cleanup. Sustained ranking improvements require consistent effort across profile management, reviews, and location content.

Businesses track success through Google Business Profile insights showing impressions, clicks, and direction requests. Rankings for "\[service\] near me" queries and specific area terms indicate improving local visibility. Ultimately, phone calls and enquiries from local searches demonstrate ROI.

